            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "If we can reliably do this, I think it will help users discover Hot Reload and provide feedback to signal a hot reload is completed. The latter was an issue observed in the most recent study session where the participant complained that he had to look for clues of completing a hot reload in the console.  It's hard to tell when there were messages from previous hot reloads in the console.",
